{"tid":1330642,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"英華女校 老師被捕後學校常有藍絲踩場抗議","createTime":"2019-07-18T15:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T17:51:08.000Z","uid":264197,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf22951690b3d52096ce135bdbd16ac113d7be43","tid":1330642,"uid":264197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VhqEPgX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVhqEPgX.png&h=bc3fcfbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英華女校 自上月有校內學生拍片控告老師和學校「太黃」<br />\n7.7 遊行又有老師因涉及「女商人」事件被捕<br />\n<br />\n聽校內老師的消息 這段日子經常有藍絲來踩場 在校門抗議示威<br />\n控告學校是散播暴力 要求要炒左個老師<br />\n又控訴關校長在校內散播黃絲言論<br />\n更有校內的消息即日內就被上傳至網上<br />\n<br />\n校內的教職員和同學都受到很大的壓力 <br />\n但校長仍然表明 學校是可以自由發表言論的地方 讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日又有藍絲到訪 還有狗車在場坐鎮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持英華女校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7983bb2b62b49d51cc7a08327c84974d3dbb9009","tid":1330642,"uid":264197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28b9a355d0b1485902a405573dfd1c5d3a82574b","tid":1330642,"uid":264197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9462242bc53b21e921610b2e25c0696336c99528","tid":1330642,"uid":263219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:55:16.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"eea3d07c206ba07ff01fea6dd9c2f3cd1ceab7b3","tid":1330642,"uid":264197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:56:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1f9452e6859d7c75eed81062cf610f9885b647b","tid":1330642,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"